                Log in to Canvas and start working through the course
                introduction module. Some of the assignments in this module 
                are part of your Engagement grade and will help you navigate
                this course. In this module, you will also learn more about the 
                course setup and expectations. In addition, if you have not
                had math in a while or struggle with Algebraic, Precalculus concepts, I 
                would recommend reviewing the items in the Review Module.
                You should have a good understanding of the concepts in this 
                module before starting this course.</p>
